Titolo: The Legend of Heroes: Trails of Cold Steel III

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: The Legend of Heroes: Trails of Cold Steel III is a role-playing video game developed by Nihon Falcom. The game is a part of the Trails series, itself a part of the larger The Legend of Heroes series, and serves as a direct sequel to The Legend of Heroes: Trails of Cold Steel II. The game was released for the PlayStation 4 in Japan in September 2017 and worldwide in October 2019. Ports for Nintendo Switch and Microsoft Windows were released in 2020. A direct sequel, The Legend of Heroes: Trails of Cold Steel IV, was released in late 2018.

Genere: Role-playing 

Valutazione: 83
